text: Craighead House may refer to: ;in Canada *Craighead House, Vancouver, British Columbia, designed by Charles Edward Pratt ;in New Zealand *Craighead, Timaru, the heritage-registered administration building of Craighead Diocesan School ;in the United States *Craighead–Jackson House, Knoxville, Tennessee, NRHP- listed *Craighead House (Nashville, Tennessee), historic house with notable gardens
title: Craighead House
